00:20:43.827 --> 00:20:45.350
So I wake up.

00:20:45.350 --> 00:20:47.140
I get dressed.

00:20:47.140 --> 00:20:48.070
I go out.

00:20:48.070 --> 00:20:49.233
I do things.

