00:21:08.280 --> 00:21:09.930
and tell them what I'm doing.

00:21:09.930 --> 00:21:12.580
I think it'd be great for
them to see what I'm doing.

00:21:14.820 --> 00:21:16.720
It takes time to build relationships.

00:21:16.720 --> 00:21:19.530
It takes time to touch base with people

00:21:19.530 --> 00:21:22.440
so I don't want another relationship;

00:21:22.440 --> 00:21:25.270
I just wanna have a relationship

00:21:25.270 --> 00:21:28.400
with somebody that I
never have to talk to,

00:21:28.400 --> 00:21:30.920
that can just follow me and see

00:21:30.920 --> 00:21:33.947
me having a relationship with...

00:21:35.200 --> 00:21:36.043
Hello.

