01:08:14.710 --> 01:08:16.340
and just to get the app in there

01:08:16.340 --> 01:08:18.600
was this whole process of negotiation,

01:08:18.600 --> 01:08:21.510
and then by doing so,
maybe I've outsmarted Apple

01:08:21.510 --> 01:08:25.460
and I've gotten my slightly
subversive app into their store

01:08:25.460 --> 01:08:29.010
but I'm holding up and
continuing this system

01:08:29.010 --> 01:08:32.120
where they get to say which
software is acceptable to users,

01:08:32.120 --> 01:08:34.020
which is appropriate and which is not.

01:08:36.670 --> 01:08:40.610
- One of the points that comes
up in Seanna's presentation

01:08:40.610 --> 01:08:42.950
that's echoed in a couple of the others

01:08:42.950 --> 01:08:47.090
is the idea that freedom
is a concept that evolves,

01:08:47.090 --> 01:08:49.850
it isn't just a thing or a fixed moment.

01:08:49.850 --> 01:08:52.520
In the legal sense,
it's a set of principles

01:08:52.520 --> 01:08:56.880
that evolve and change in
time, in a disciplinary sense

01:08:56.880 --> 01:08:59.720
the arts as we know
them go through changes

01:08:59.720 --> 01:09:03.540
agreed on by larger audiences
or members of the community

01:09:03.540 --> 01:09:07.030
and I'm just wondering
how that kind of a notion

01:09:07.030 --> 01:09:10.120
might relate to where
and how those communities

01:09:10.120 --> 01:09:15.120
sit within cities physically,
including the idea

01:09:15.720 --> 01:09:18.170
of the arts themselves
as evolving communities

01:09:18.170 --> 01:09:20.940
in different parts of the
city, and the relative degrees

01:09:20.940 --> 01:09:24.513
to which freedom are or aren't
available to those members.

01:09:25.920 --> 01:09:28.950
- The part where you said,
for me, underlying that

01:09:28.950 --> 01:09:33.950
is sort of something that is
perhaps more foundational,

01:09:34.620 --> 01:09:38.100
and that goes back to
the closing points of

01:09:38.100 --> 01:09:39.730
Seanna's presentation, the closing point

01:09:39.730 --> 01:09:42.570
of Andrea's presentation, so Seanna,

01:09:42.570 --> 01:09:45.880
