01:15:58.700 --> 01:16:00.610
how we internalize and regurgitate

01:16:00.610 --> 01:16:04.113
capitalism and other
oppressive institutions?

01:16:05.272 --> 01:16:06.170
So in a sense, how can we critique

01:16:06.170 --> 01:16:08.010
when we are in Plato's cave

01:16:08.010 --> 01:16:10.573
and perhaps have no real
conception of freedom?

01:16:12.100 --> 01:16:13.140
- I couldn't understand...

01:16:13.140 --> 01:16:15.256
- I think the first part of the question

01:16:15.256 --> 01:16:18.610
